Class ConfigValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • helper.ConfigValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<ConfigValue>

    public final class ConfigValue
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ConfigValue>
    Represents a single configuration value used to exchange data beween modules, between a module and a control interface and to store configuration data in the database.
